🎯 Final Goal

When you’ve imported all relevant resources, you’ll run:

terraform plan


and see:

No changes. Your infrastructure matches the configuration.


That means Terraform now fully manages your Auth0 tenant — from apps to APIs to branding — 100% IaC.
